title: How to Stop Being Mediocre
itunes:title: How to Stop Being Mediocre
description:
Episode 622 - Every person, deep down inside, has the fear of not fitting in. The problem with that is that if we want to live extraordinary lives, we must stand out. So how do we balance these two opposites so that we can stand out and create the life that we want? Well, in this episode, I will tell you how! Follow me on Instagram at https://instagram.com/robdialjr
